39
00:04:48,220 --> 00:04:48,990
Come out.

40
00:04:57,750 --> 00:04:59,990
Which one is more surprising

41
00:05:00,710 --> 00:05:01,820
yours or mine?

42
00:05:05,020 --> 00:05:05,820
sis

43
