60
00:06:07,430 --> 00:06:08,310
What about me?

61
00:06:08,710 --> 00:06:12,150
I was looking for a chance to confess to you.

62
00:06:12,630 --> 00:06:13,500
Confess?

63
00:06:17,150 --> 00:06:18,780
