82
00:07:29,740 --> 00:07:32,860
♫ I miss you again when the wind blows ♫

83
00:07:34,830 --> 00:07:39,130
♫ But I’m not willing to tell you ♫

84
00:07:42,100 --> 00:07:42,940
Today is

85
