178
00:14:02,900 --> 00:14:04,140
You’re talented.

179
00:14:04,310 --> 00:14:05,440
Would you like a try?

180
00:14:05,580 --> 00:14:07,040
I don’t need a competition

181
00:14:07,100 --> 00:14:08,660
to prove my talent.

182
00:14:08,890 --> 00:14:11,090
