221
00:17:01,200 --> 00:17:02,120
♫ Blink my eyes ♫

222
00:17:02,120 --> 00:17:04,319
♫ Like you are here ♫

223
00:17:05,140 --> 00:17:06,940
♫ These sweet little secrets ♫

224
00:17:06,940 --> 00:17:09,540
♫ The sweet you and me ♫

225
00:17:09,540 --> 00:17:10,930
