226
00:17:10,930 --> 00:17:12,579
♫ A whole forest of secret love ♫

227
00:17:12,579 --> 00:17:13,260
Is it sweet?

228
00:17:13,630 --> 00:17:14,300
Sour.

229
00:17:14,290 --> 00:17:15,170
♫ Memories that belong to us ♫

230
00:17:15,170 --> 00:17:17,410
♫ Grows a bit densely ♫

231
00:17:17,720 --> 00:17:20,220
♫ I treasure everything ♫

232
00:17:20,220 --> 00:17:20,990
Wait a second.

233
00:17:20,990 --> 00:17:23,130
♫ The sweet you and me ♫

234
00:17:23,130 --> 00:17:25,200
♫ No more ice in our relationship ♫

235
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:27,220
♫ Everything is very comfortable ♫

236
00:17:28,750 --> 00:17:30,150
I’ve got a unique skill,

237
00:17:30,330 --> 00:17:31,870
