244
00:18:10,300 --> 00:18:11,500
Take up the notebook.

245
00:18:19,550 --> 00:18:20,350
Write it down.

246
00:18:21,750 --> 00:18:23,410
Boyfriend’s privilege No.1,

247
00:18:23,420 --> 00:18:26,150
you mustn’t lie to me,
under whatever condition.

248
00:18:26,420 --> 00:18:27,280
I swear I won’t!

249
00:18:27,990 --> 00:18:29,580
Boyfriend’s privilege No.2,

250
00:18:29,580 --> 00:18:30,910
no matter what happens,

251
00:18:31,570 --> 00:18:33,170
you mustn’t break up with me.

252
00:18:33,220 --> 00:18:34,220
I promise I won’t!

253
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:36,330
Boyfriend’s privilege No.3,

254
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:37,670
in case of any problem,

255
00:18:37,910 --> 00:18:39,240
come to me immediately.

256
00:18:39,390 --> 00:18:40,100
No problem.

257
00:18:41,750 --> 00:18:42,420
Sit down.

258
00:18:50,100 --> 00:18:51,030
Privilege No.4,

259
00:18:53,100 --> 00:18:54,340
answer the phone

260
00:18:54,390 --> 00:18:55,920
and text back immediately.

261
00:18:56,630 --> 00:18:57,560
Privilege No.5,

262
00:18:58,100 --> 00:18:59,540
when you’re out of classes,

263
00:18:59,540 --> 00:19:00,750
tell me where you are

264
00:19:00,980 --> 00:19:02,310
and come when I need you.

265
00:19:02,700 --> 00:19:03,630
Privilege No. 6,

266
00:19:03,990 --> 00:19:06,260
treat me differently
from how you treat other boys.

267
00:19:06,260 --> 00:19:07,190
Privilege No. 7,

268
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:11,030
the gift for me must be unique.

269
00:19:14,100 --> 00:19:14,910
Finished?

270
00:19:15,460 --> 00:19:16,150
Yes.

271
00:19:16,390 --> 00:19:19,550
I’ve recorded them very completely.

272
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:23,870
