276
00:19:37,340 --> 00:19:38,090
Which item?

277
00:19:50,670 --> 00:19:52,550
Hello, my girlfriend,

278
00:19:53,870 --> 00:19:54,580
Ye Weimian.

279
00:19:55,420 --> 00:19:58,550
Hello, my kind and demure boyfriend,

280
00:19:58,790 --> 00:20:00,150
Face-saving Gu.

281
00:20:25,060 --> 00:20:26,860
